    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Apricity 的世界是由废墟与杂草丛生的运河构成的庞大网络，灵感源自英国文物遗产。在 Apricity，大自然重新夺回大地，昔日繁盛的王国早已崩塌成瓦砾。神秘的怪物与奇异的生物潜伏于阴影之中。需要你对抗自然的怒潮，击败黑暗，为世界重现光明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/14f612dcfee60be87b1f3511484e9a5c.poster.avif?t=1759222469\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/14f612dcfee60be87b1f3511484e9a5c.webm?t=1759222469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 通过烹调组合出强力升级</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 调配能灼烧、冰冻、电击、诅咒敌人的配方！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 爆炸性、快节奏的砍杀战斗</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/8b383eb0e13f0bddc85b9c22391033c0.poster.avif?t=1759222469\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/8b383eb0e13f0bddc85b9c22391033c0.webm?t=1759222469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 发掘暗藏秘辛，解锁奖励</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 发现独特的怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 探索精心打造的特色场景</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/246778c5e8e764bb37b074e1977654b4.poster.avif?t=1759222469\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/246778c5e8e764bb37b074e1977654b4.webm?t=1759222469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 寻找并种植强效的蘑菇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 在深水中钓鱼以强化你的配方</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 收集灵魂并推动你的进程</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/db2d3ac32063d41923c1b0a651d1fbdb.poster.avif?t=1759222469\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037650/extras/db2d3ac32063d41923c1b0a651d1fbdb.webm?t=1759222469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 结交同伴并肩作战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 建造属于你的避风港</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
